<br>
There is a problem with polls...<br>
<br>
Anyone can vote in them as long as they have a global EZboard account.  So people could be dropping by and voting, never posting yet influencing the polls at will.  One person could ostensibly vote as many times as they have free accounts.<br>
<br>
